Which Attributes

Source: R/bugphyzz.R
whichAttr.Rd

whichAttr shows which attributes are present in a dataset imported with importBugphyzz. Signatures created with getBugphyzzSignatures would take these names.

whichAttr(bp)

Arguments

bp

A data.frame imported with importBugphyzz.

Value

A character vector.

Examples


bp <- importBugphyzz()
#> Using data downloaded on 2024-01-04 05:32:02.
